#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.73"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.73:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.73:0.2"
msgid "8. Sammappadhānavagga"
msgstr "8. Right Efforts"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 73. Sikkhasutta → sikkhādubbalyadhammappadhānasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an9.73:0.3"
msgid "73. Sikkhasutta"
msgstr "73. Weaknesses in Training and Effort"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.73:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, sikkhādubbalyāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five weaknesses when you’re training."

msgctxt "an9.73:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an9.73:1.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipāto … pe … surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Killing living creatures, stealing, sexual misconduct, lying, and using "
"alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "an9.73:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca sikkhādubbalyāni."
msgstr "These are the five weaknesses when you’re training."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.73:2.1"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ sikkhādubbalyānaṃ pahānāya cattāro "
"sammappadhānā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr ""
"To give up these five weaknesses in your training you should develop the "
"four right efforts."

msgctxt "an9.73:2.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an9.73:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anuppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"anuppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti "
"padahati;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant generates enthusiasm, tries, makes an effort, exerts "
"the mind, and strives so that bad, unskillful qualities don’t arise."

msgctxt "an9.73:2.4"
msgid ""
"uppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati "
"vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati;"
msgstr ""
"They generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so "
"that bad, unskillful qualities that have arisen are given up."

msgctxt "an9.73:2.5"
msgid ""
"anuppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ uppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ "
"ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati;"
msgstr ""
"They generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so "
"that skillful qualities arise."

msgctxt "an9.73:2.6"
msgid ""
"uppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ ṭhitiyā asammosāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya "
"bhāvanāya pāripūriyā chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ "
"paggaṇhāti padahati."
msgstr ""
"They generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so "
"that skillful qualities that have arisen remain, are not lost, but "
"increase, mature, and are completed by development."

msgctxt "an9.73:2.7"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ sikkhādubbalyānaṃ pahānāya ime cattāro "
"sammappadhānā bhāvetabbā”ti."
msgstr ""
"To give up those five weaknesses in your training you should develop these "
"four right efforts.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.73:2.8"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
